I can provide you with the current weather in Seattle.

To get the current weather, I will call the `get_weather` function with the location as "Seattle" and the unit as "celsius".

```json
{
  "type": "function",
  "name": "get_weather",
  "parameters": {
    "location": "Seattle",
    "unit": "celsius"
  }
}
```

